requirements.description:
No admin instrumentation module exists. An InstrumentedServer class is needed that:
      (a) registers a /admin namespace on the parent Socket.IO server with a connect handler
          that enforces the configured auth policy;
      (b) emits initial state events (config, all_sockets, server_stats) to each newly
          connected admin client;
      (c) runs a background task that periodically re-emits server_stats to all admin clients;
      (d) exposes shutdown(), uninstrument(), and _check_for_upgrade to support test lifecycle
          management.
